Diagnostic commands

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector diagnose [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  orphans       Diagnose orphan notes (no incoming + no outgoing links)
  broken-links  Diagnose broken links (unresolved and ambiguous)
  help          Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -o, --output <FORMAT>  Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -h, --help             Print help
